  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 4px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;text-align: center;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4212962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100000984\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a5b9c5a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhWYwgGR0y5icGiaJicgnF0NEeEfcgESc5vefTacdk6jzCrTwibib2yGy7xJ6wtB7mqDJLCMCR5n2hSxfpib1uKS2qMgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 16px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">今天，美团 LongCat 团队正式对外发布并开源&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">LongCat-Flash-Thinking-2601</span>。作为已发布的 LongCat-Flash-Thinking 模型的升级版，LongCat-Flash-Thinking-2601在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agentic Search（智能体搜索）</span>、<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agentic Tool Use（智能体工具调用）</span>、<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">TIR（工具交互推理）</span>等核心评测基准上，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">均达到开源模型 SOTA 水平</span>。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">该模型尤其在工具调用上表现出卓越的泛化能力，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">在依赖工具调用的随机复杂任务中性能超越了 Claude</span>，可大幅度降低真实场景下新工具的适配训练成本；同时它是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">首个完整开源并支持在线免费体验「重思考模式」的模型</span>，同时启动 8 个大脑飞速运转，确保思考周全、决策可靠。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">目前该功能已经可以在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://longcat.ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://longcat.ai</a></span>网站免费体验（仅选择深度思考功能时会触发重思考模式）。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 572px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"205\" data-backw=\"568\" data-ratio=\"0.36018518518518516\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;vertical-align: middle;width: 572px;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f98112c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhWYwgGR0y5icGiaJicgnF0NEeEfcgESc5vebNlvxq0mjia6fZ2LuSzszppWBMlLgtqHLWuAfEeBKs3hZ9XlLOT1QRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 572px;height: auto;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29325259515570934\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1156\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;vertical-align: middle;width: 572px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/hWYwgGR0y5icGiaJicgnF0NEeEfcgESc5ven3mv9NDqen0lufkBLvvSGKcPvyXNfn1n8Mfy724TYakiaUG0kSZCM3w/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"568\" data-cropsely2=\"167\" data-imgfileid=\"100000985\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b1639b46&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhWYwgGR0y5icGiaJicgnF0NEeEfcgESc5ven3mv9NDqen0lufkBLvvSGKcPvyXNfn1n8Mfy724TYakiaUG0kSZCM3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 4px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">全新升级的「重思考」模式，让模型学会了“深思熟虑”再行动，遇到高难度问题时，模型会把思考过程拆成并行思考和总结归纳两步来做：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">并行思考阶段，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">模型会同时独立梳理出好几条推理路径，就跟人面对难题时会琢磨不同解法一个道理，还会特意保证思路的多样性，生怕漏掉最优解；</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">总结归纳阶段，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">对多条路径进行梳理、优化与合成，并将优化结果重新输入，形成闭环迭代推理，推动思考持续深化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">除此之外，研究团队还专门设计了额外的强化学习环节，针对性打磨模型的总结归纳能力，让 LongCat-Flash-Thinking-2601 真正实现“想清楚再行动”。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 572px;height: auto;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23333333333333334\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;vertical-align: middle;width: 572px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b7d5a8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhWYwgGR0y5icGiaJicgnF0NEeEfcgESc5veoAvILtZ2awwEQYia7qwCmPpA3L2ntVxxbEZQaTciapyibl0Frny19uVWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 4px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">经过全面严谨的评估显示，LongCat-Flash-Thinking-2601 模型在编程、数学推理、智能体工具调用、智能体搜索维度表现全面领先：</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 572px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5731481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;vertical-align: middle;width: 572px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3ab3778&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhWYwgGR0y5icGiaJicgnF0NEeEfcgESc5ve36XOzD73zHzuiawTIbhicCMLa8JqI30gOIiafM5ic64WQwToc4ViacAo9eQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:默认, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 4px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-decoration-style:init